      <pubDate>Tue, 01 Oct 2024 15:48:52 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>长滩港可以处理更多货物</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2024-10-01/port-of-long-beach-can-handle-more-cargo-says-director</link>
      <description><![CDATA[长滩港执行董事马里奥·科尔德罗 (Mario Cordero) 谈到码头工人罢工对美国东海岸和墨西哥湾沿岸的影响。科尔德罗表示，他的港口可以处理因停工而涌入的任何集装箱。他正在接受“彭博未平仓合约”的采访。（来源：彭博）]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2024-10-01/port-of-long-beach-can-handle-more-cargo-says-director</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 01 Oct 2024 15:48:47 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>美联储库克认为人工智能将对劳动力市场和生产力产生“巨大”影响</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2024-10-01/fed-s-cook-sees-substantial-ai-impact-on-labor-markets-productivity</link>
      <description><![CDATA[美联储理事丽莎·库克表示，她看到“越来越多的证据表明人工智能将对美国和全球劳动力市场产生重大影响”，并预计人工智能将推动生产率增长。库克周二在亚特兰大、波士顿和里士满联邦储备银行组织的会议上发表了讲话。（来源：彭博社）]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2024-10-01/fed-s-cook-sees-substantial-ai-impact-on-labor-markets-productivity</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 01 Oct 2024 15:41:26 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>印度批准采取措施遏制股票衍生品交易热潮</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-01/india-clears-steps-to-curb-trading-rush-in-stock-derivatives</link>
      <description><![CDATA[由于散户参与度不断提高，投机性赌注达到全球最高水平，印度证券监管机构周二出台了新措施，限制该国股票衍生品交易的激增。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-01/india-clears-steps-to-curb-trading-rush-in-stock-derivatives</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 01 Oct 2024 12:59:38 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
